long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The ShopTach Chrome Extension is a powerful tool designed to enhance your experience with the ShopTach platform. Seamlessly integrated into your Chrome browser, this extension empowers automotive repair shops to efficiently collect new contact information and manage Work in Progress (WIP) orders without ever leaving the browser environment.
